projects.name: Google Shopping Scraping
projects.description: This Python project allows you to scrape product information from Google Shopping and save the data in both Excel and JSON formats. You can specify search options such as minimum and maximum price, shipping availability, and product sorting.

projects.name: Quiz Up Platform
